name: The Portal of Life / Experiment 7
description:
"The Portal of Life" is a visual project that began after doing about 6 experiments with abstract compositions. In fact, the portal of life is my Experiment number 7 and It refers to that place that we all know, beyond what is known and identified or comfortable, but that very few times we decide to inhabit and sustain ourselves there.

It is a sensory game with nears, touches, distances, illuminations and opacities... its alive.
